<div id="about-the-community" class="section-spacer">
    <h2 class="sect-title">About Sandstone Valley</h2>
    <div class="col-grid-2">
        <div>
            <p class="par-lg">A master-planned, family-oriented neighborhood, the community in Sandstone features a myriad of housing options for the discerning homebuyer and real estate investors alike.</p>
            <p class="par-lg">While the development for the Sandstone Valley began back in 1982, it has only recently been completed.</p>
            <p class="par-lg">Homes for sale in Sandstone include townhomes, and condominiums with the former readily listed at prices ranging from $250,000 to $550,000 and the latter available for a price somewhere between $250,000 and $400,000.</p>
